00:20:39,250 --> 00:20:41,550
[Missing Person: Xie He'an]

294
00:20:39,470 --> 00:20:40,580
This is my daughter.

295
00:20:41,650 --> 00:20:42,760
The day she disappeared,

296
00:20:43,170 --> 00:20:44,680
she was wearing this pair of hairpins.

297
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:47,210
Did you make the hairpins too?

298
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:51,820
She loved them.

299
00:20:52,970 --> 00:20:53,830
She wore them every day.

300
00:20:55,330 --> 00:20:56,810
May I ask, how old was she?

301
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:00,760
Nine years old.

302
00:21:02,260 --> 00:21:02,750
So young.

303
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:08,090
Do you sleep here all the time?

304
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:11,920
Most of the time.

305
00:21:34,170 --> 00:21:35,950
I'm really sorry

306
00:21:36,710 --> 00:21:37,820
to have to tell you so much.

307
00:21:43,290 --> 00:21:44,270
One.

308
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:47,160
Three.

309
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:48,150
Four.

310
00:21:52,140 --> 00:21:52,530
Ms. He,

311
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:54,320
are there seven dolls?

312
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:56,160
There isn't just one doll, right?

313
00:22:00,810 --> 00:22:01,430
Seven.

314
00:22:03,980 --> 00:22:05,110
Every year

315
00:22:05,710 --> 00:22:07,940
I'd imagine how she'd look a year older

316
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:10,440
and make a doll.

317
00:22:11,030 --> 00:22:12,810
I hope that there'd be someone who'd walk by the window

318
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,430
and tell us that

319
00:22:16,070 --> 00:22:18,480
he saw a little girl who looked the same somewhere.

320
00:22:20,250 --> 00:22:21,520
But my husband didn't want to.

321
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:24,120
So I just kept them all in there.

322
00:22:33,410 --> 00:22:34,750
We're leaving now.

323
00:22:35,490 --> 00:22:35,980
Will you be here

324
00:22:37,420 --> 00:22:38,660
again?

325
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,130
You'll come here again, right?

326
00:22:48,350 --> 00:22:49,750
The ground was covered with dust.

327
00:22:50,170 --> 00:22:51,870
Everyone who lives there gets sick.

328
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:55,190
Why didn't you tell Ms. He you saw her?

329
00:22:57,170 --> 00:22:58,480
Don't give hope to people

330
00:22:58,760 --> 00:22:59,850
who have lost their family members.

331
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,200
License.

332
00:23:17,730 --> 00:23:18,670
Isn't it too sweet?

333
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:20,030
No.

334
00:23:20,260 --> 00:23:20,990
It's delicious.

335
00:23:28,970 --> 00:23:29,970
Do you have any black coffee?

336
00:23:31,490 --> 00:23:32,500
I have water from the ditch. Want that?

337
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:34,440
You gonna help me shine a light on it or not?

338
00:23:37,090 --> 00:23:37,740
Below.

339
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:39,390
Below.

340
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,070
I asked you to shine a light on it, but you didn't.

341
00:23:49,570 --> 00:23:50,570
And you're eating cake.

342
00:23:54,150 --> 00:23:54,660
It's hooked.

343
00:24:20,530 --> 00:24:21,270
It's sweet, right?

344
00:24:22,150 --> 00:24:23,160
So it's not my problem.

345
00:24:23,180 --> 00:24:23,930
It's really sweet.

346
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:25,710
I think you have a problem with your taste, too.

347
00:24:26,910 --> 00:24:27,670
Who's it from?

348
00:24:28,290 --> 00:24:28,880
Wasn't I

349
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:31,280
assigned by the director

350
00:24:31,310 --> 00:24:32,110
to support the youth project?

351
00:24:32,620 --> 00:24:33,610
How'd we know?

352
00:24:34,700 --> 00:24:35,700
Anyway, at that event

353
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:36,930
I met a cake maker.

354
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:38,510
He took the cakes to the station

355
00:24:38,820 --> 00:24:39,500
and said they were low in sugar.

356
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,190
Are the police allowed to accept gifts?

357
00:24:42,330 --> 00:24:43,060
What gift?

358
00:24:43,910 --> 00:24:44,650
Just a taste test.

359
00:24:46,810 --> 00:24:48,090
Isn't it said that eating sweet things would make your mood better?

360
00:24:49,320 --> 00:24:52,200
-Because a rapid rise in blood sugar stimulates insulin... -Just say yes.

361
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:02,250
Have some, punk.

362
00:25:02,780 --> 00:25:03,600
I can't help it.

363
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,070
Just take it as medicine.

364
00:25:06,690 --> 00:25:07,100
Guangyan.

365
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:08,450
Hold him down.

366
00:25:08,700 --> 00:25:09,000
Okay.

367
00:25:16,330 --> 00:25:17,390
Take a big bite.

368
00:25:17,850 --> 00:25:18,430
Childish.

369
00:25:24,580 --> 00:25:25,330
Why are you blushing?

370
00:25:48,490 --> 00:25:49,500
So that woman

371
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:51,060
made me according to how her child looked like.

372
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:53,900
Why?

373
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:56,060
What?

374
00:25:56,730 --> 00:25:57,690
I'm not her daughter.

375
00:25:58,460 --> 00:25:59,330
Why should I accept

376
00:25:59,360 --> 00:26:00,840
that woman's feelings and emotions?

377
00:26:01,330 --> 00:26:02,370
You wouldn't be here without her.

378
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,240
Did she ask me?

379
00:26:04,330 --> 00:26:06,390
I didn't want to be born as a substitute.

380
00:26:11,260 --> 00:26:12,330
I don't want to be stuck there.

381
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,910
That woman made me miserable and confused.

382
00:26:16,850 --> 00:26:18,660
I'm not even sure what I look like.

383
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:27,760
I can't even get rid of this annoying hairpin.

384
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:34,560
How can we help you?

385
00:26:36,620 --> 00:26:37,560
Find her daughter

386
00:26:38,870 --> 00:26:39,760
and let me go.

387
00:26:42,290 --> 00:26:43,370
We're already working on it.

388
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:45,420
A kidnapping case from seven years ago

389
00:26:45,820 --> 00:26:46,350
is hard,

390
00:26:46,850 --> 00:26:47,420
very hard.

391
00:26:48,300 --> 00:26:49,430
But the harder the case, the bigger the credit.

392
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:52,460
Good things happen when I'm with you.

393
00:26:55,510 --> 00:26:56,080
Senior.

394
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:57,750
I'm One-per.

395
00:26:57,910 --> 00:26:58,980
No, I'm Chuying.

396
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:00,810
I have a favor to ask you.

397
00:27:02,030 --> 00:27:02,410
Yes.

398
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:05,350
She didn't mean that.

399
00:27:06,150 --> 00:27:07,680
Does it matter if she meant it or not?

400
00:27:08,420 --> 00:27:09,740
The end result is the same anyway.

401
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:11,510
Yes.

402
00:27:12,500 --> 00:27:13,340
You'll do anything

403
00:27:13,370 --> 00:27:14,430
to get what you want.

404
00:27:27,490 --> 00:27:28,030
Turn away.

405
00:27:31,210 --> 00:27:32,320
With your head!

406
00:27:39,660 --> 00:27:40,240
I found it.

407
00:27:47,320 --> 00:27:48,450
They only reported the case afterwards.

408
00:27:48,470 --> 00:27:49,510
The clues were really insufficient.

409
00:27:49,850 --> 00:27:50,910
And it's been so long.

410
00:27:51,300 --> 00:27:52,740
Maybe it's just that it's taken so long

411
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:54,530
for so many things to come to light.

412
00:27:55,260 --> 00:27:55,710
Whatever.

413
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:56,870
Let me take a look first.

414
00:27:57,300 --> 00:27:57,900
Promise me,

415
00:27:58,540 --> 00:27:59,820
just look at it, don't think of taking it away.

416
00:28:01,670 --> 00:28:02,700
You're not taking it seriously.

417
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:25,230
She looks like a cop.

418
00:28:27,980 --> 00:28:29,070
She really does.

419
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:31,890
I wasn't so hopeful just by looking at her face,

420
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:33,850
but now it looks like something.

421
00:28:37,750 --> 00:28:40,250
Sometimes, when I see her in her police uniform, I would think

422
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:41,570
she's just role-playing.

423
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:44,540
But where did she get the whiteboard from?

424
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:47,820
This is from our calligraphy classroom.

425
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:49,660
Why are you whispering so loud?

426
00:28:50,250 --> 00:28:51,090
I risked my life

427
00:28:51,120 --> 00:28:51,990
to get you these files.

428
00:28:53,170 --> 00:28:53,560
Fine.

429
00:28:53,930 --> 00:28:54,540
Don't look into anything.

430
00:28:55,070 --> 00:28:55,870
I'm sorry.

431
00:29:02,950 --> 00:29:03,580
Xie He'an.

432
00:29:03,820 --> 00:29:04,390
She's nine years old

433
00:29:04,580 --> 00:29:05,450
and in the third grade of primary school.

434
00:29:05,940 --> 00:29:06,960
She walked to and from school.

435
00:29:07,220 --> 00:29:07,850
Every day after school,

436
00:29:07,870 --> 00:29:09,650
she would go to He Shouzheng's studio.

437
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,400
The time was not fixed.

438
00:29:11,990 --> 00:29:13,490
But she would arrive by three o'clock at the latest.

439
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:15,600
Mom, I'm back.

440
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:18,290
Why didn't you come straight back home?

441
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:19,440
Where did you go?

442
00:29:37,100 --> 00:29:37,590
Hello.

443
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,840
On the evening of the kidnapping,

444
00:29:40,210 --> 00:29:41,990
He Shoutang got a call with a voice changer,

445
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,880
claiming that Xie He'an had been kidnapped by them,

446
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:45,100
and they're asking for a ransom of 5 million.

447
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:47,580
And he threatened to kill her child immediately

448
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:48,430
if they call the police.

449
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:51,230
Proof of the child's possession

450
00:29:51,590 --> 00:29:53,110
was the doll charm

451
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:55,350
[The only exhibit]

452
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:55,250
from Xie He'an's backpack that

453
00:29:55,510 --> 00:29:56,480
dropped off in the studio's mailbox.

454
00:30:04,650 --> 00:30:06,080
He Shoutang and her husband, Xie Hui

455
00:30:06,100 --> 00:30:07,270
only raised 3 million

456
00:30:07,290 --> 00:30:08,420
in two days.

457
00:30:08,860 --> 00:30:10,330
After bargaining with the kidnappers,

458
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:11,410
the ransom money

459
00:30:12,250 --> 00:30:13,490
was placed on this road.

460
00:30:23,940 --> 00:30:25,680
The kidnappers agreed to release Xie He'an

461
00:30:25,930 --> 00:30:27,180
after they received the ransom

462
00:30:27,380 --> 00:30:28,760
and made sure they didn't call the police.

463
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:31,540
But after that, they haven't heard from them.

464
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:33,640
Only then they called the police.

465
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,160
Since they didn't call the police,

466
00:30:38,370 --> 00:30:40,270
within a week of the incident,

467
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:42,200
the investigating police had very few leads

468
00:30:42,220 --> 00:30:43,850
about the kidnappers.

469
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:48,070
These are all the people who were interviewed at the time,

470
00:30:48,780 --> 00:30:50,060
including Xie He'an's parents.

471
00:30:50,490 --> 00:30:51,640
They were all questioned at the time.

472
00:30:52,470 --> 00:30:52,920
Why?

473
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,980
We can't rule out that they're putting up a show for this child abuse.

474
00:31:00,050 --> 00:31:01,570
These two are He Shoutang's employees.

475
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:04,550
One was a fine arts undergraduate at the time.

476
00:31:04,780 --> 00:31:05,900
One was a single mother

477
00:31:06,530 --> 00:31:07,550
with a teenage daughter.

478
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:08,990
Her daughter was Xie He'an's senior at school.

479
00:31:10,350 --> 00:31:12,110
Xie Hui's coworkers and their neighbors

480
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:14,060
have all been investigated.

481
00:31:17,290 --> 00:31:17,770
Guangyan.

482
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:19,230
Guangyan.

483
00:31:20,300 --> 00:31:20,990
Cao Guangyan, what are you doing?

484
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:23,090
I'm more used to reading words.

485
00:31:24,150 --> 00:31:26,160
Case files are classified. I don't even have access to them.

486
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:27,390
How can you

487
00:31:27,420 --> 00:31:28,540
go through it casually like this?

488
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,160
Besides, the group leader is speaking.

489
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:31,330
Do you, a group member, have any manners?

490
00:31:31,910 --> 00:31:33,440
What group member? What are you talking about?

491
00:31:33,930 --> 00:31:35,040
And if you couldn't get it, why did you have it?

492
00:31:37,590 --> 00:31:38,120
Turn away.

493
00:31:47,870 --> 00:31:48,800
Why are you asking so much?

494
00:31:54,140 --> 00:31:54,970
Who is this person?

495
00:31:56,130 --> 00:31:56,860
Zhao Baisi.

496
00:31:57,530 --> 00:31:58,850
He's Xie He'an's father's colleague.

497
00:31:58,920 --> 00:31:59,980
On the day of the kidnapping,

498
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:01,540
he had dinner with the craft store employee, Lin Jingmei,

499
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:02,920
the single mother

500
00:32:02,950 --> 00:32:03,820
with a daughter

501
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:05,150
we were talking about.

502
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:07,350
He's a witness of Lin Jingmei's alibi.

503
00:32:08,430 --> 00:32:09,230
You memorised it so fast?

504
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,760
I've seen this person a few times.

505
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:18,620
In the shop?

506
00:32:20,100 --> 00:32:20,660
No.

507
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,850
So...

508
00:32:36,520 --> 00:32:38,320
Is there any news on what happened to He'an?

509
00:32:39,100 --> 00:32:40,810
So far we've just reviewed the documents.

510
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,240
I hope we can find a new direction.

511
00:32:45,860 --> 00:32:47,000
I'm sorry for taking up so much of your time

512
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:48,130
for something that happened so long ago.

513
00:32:48,620 --> 00:32:49,700
You must be very busy at work.

514
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:51,320
You don't have to say that.

515
00:32:51,760 --> 00:32:53,880
I do business so my time is more flexible.

516
00:32:54,470 --> 00:32:55,410
Being able to help

517
00:32:55,430 --> 00:32:56,500
is the only thing I hope for.

518
00:32:58,810 --> 00:33:00,330
Have you contacted him

519
00:33:00,650 --> 00:33:01,700
after Xie Hui resigned?

520
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:03,660
Occasionally.

521
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:07,400
It's said in the records that

522
00:33:07,750 --> 00:33:08,950
you were a frequent visitor to his wife's craft store

523
00:33:08,970 --> 00:33:10,640
before the incident.

524
00:33:11,770 --> 00:33:12,400
On holidays,

525
00:33:12,430 --> 00:33:14,180
I used to go look for Xie Hui in the store quite often.

526
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,360
I'm jealous.

527
00:33:17,590 --> 00:33:18,550
He must be very nice.

528
00:33:19,370 --> 00:33:21,130
Otherwise, who'd want to see

529
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,670
their boss when they leave the office?

530
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:28,190
Have you been there recently?

531
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:29,210
The craft store.

532
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,580
He's been there a lot

533
00:33:33,620 --> 00:33:35,170
since He'an's incident.

534
00:33:36,050 --> 00:33:37,140
And then

535
00:33:39,260 --> 00:33:40,030
you stopped going for good?

536
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:41,570
No.

537
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,640
How many times has he been there?

538
00:33:43,660 --> 00:33:44,380
And when?

539
00:33:45,510 --> 00:33:46,200
I mean,

540
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:47,960
staring at you out there like that.

541
00:33:49,260 --> 00:33:50,010
Three times.

542
00:33:51,150 --> 00:33:52,290
I can't remember.

543
00:33:53,030 --> 00:33:55,330
But the most recent one was a few days ago.

544
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:59,130
Were you there a week ago?

545
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:02,810
A week ago,

546
00:34:03,170 --> 00:34:04,850
what brought you to his store?

547
00:34:12,199 --> 00:34:13,620
You don't have to clean up.

548
00:34:14,040 --> 00:34:14,840
I didn't invite you

549
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:15,670
here

550
00:34:15,870 --> 00:34:17,010
to do this for me.

551
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:19,250
This really puts me on the spot.

552
00:34:19,380 --> 00:34:20,560
Please stop cleaning.

553
00:34:20,650 --> 00:34:22,000
You gotta clean this up,

554
00:34:22,830 --> 00:34:23,600
or you'll get sick.

555
00:34:23,830 --> 00:34:24,420
That's what the doctor said.

556
00:34:26,050 --> 00:34:27,170
I'm not one yet.

557
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:29,260
Besides, we should be the one feeling embarrassed

558
00:34:29,330 --> 00:34:30,710
in shower caps.

559
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:31,290
This.

560
00:34:32,170 --> 00:34:34,060
Where could we have found a cooler looking bandana

561
00:34:34,250 --> 00:34:35,510
so last minute?

562
00:34:35,679 --> 00:34:36,800
Cool bandanaï¼Ÿ

563
00:34:38,370 --> 00:34:39,280
What does it look like?

564
00:34:51,909 --> 00:34:53,400
Add facial features or I can't understand.

565
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:03,210
Draw it more detailed or I can't understand.

566
00:35:08,220 --> 00:35:09,720
Add a body or I can't understand.

567
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:10,950
What exactly are you trying to understand?

568
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:29,330
Ms. He,

569
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:31,460
can I have this one?

570
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:33,980
Sure.

571
00:35:41,830 --> 00:35:42,520
It's almost done.

572
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:43,750
Thank you.

573
00:35:44,410 --> 00:35:45,480
But the bottom has not been cleaned.

574
00:35:45,520 --> 00:35:46,120
It doesn't matter.

575
00:35:46,650 --> 00:35:47,580
Take a break first.

576
00:36:02,810 --> 00:36:03,590
I'm sorry.

